trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for controls that implement the methods of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl"></xref> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Utvider utformingen virkemåte for kontroller som implementerer metoder for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl"> </xref> abstrakt klasse.

trans-unit.source: The CompositeControlDesigner can be used with other control types that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.INamingContainer> interface.
trans-unit.target: CompositeControlDesigner kan bare brukes med andre kontrolltypene som implementerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.INamingContainer>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.INamingContainer>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise CompositeControlDesigner functions similarly to its base class, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Ellers CompositeControlDesigner-funksjoner på samme måte som basisklassen, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>
Hvis du vil se et eksempel se <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates the child controls of this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter barnet kontroller av dette <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The CreateChildControls method is used to recreate the child controls in the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden av CreateChildControls brukes til å gjenopprette underordnede kontroller i den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: It ensures that the control collection is created before creating the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Det sikrer at samlingen for kontrollen er opprettet før du oppretter utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: Gets the HTML that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter HTML som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the overloads available for this method see <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om overlastingene tilgjengelig for denne metoden kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: In this overridden method, the base implementation always creates the child controls on the associated control.
trans-unit.target: I denne overstyrte metoden oppretter base implementeringen alltid barnet vises på den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The HTML that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: HTML som brukes til å representere kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the designer with the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer designer med angitt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The designer host calls Initialize to initialize the component for design.
trans-unit.target: Kall designer vert initialisere for å starte komponenten for utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation will throw an exception if the associated control does not implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.INamingContainer> interface.
trans-unit.target: Grunnleggende implementeringen Iverksett et unntak hvis den tilknyttede kontrollen ikke implementerer det <xref:System.Web.UI.INamingContainer>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.INamingContainer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref>, which is the control associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref>, som er tilknyttet utformeren kontrollen.
